| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2622 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 76da56b5-a4ae-5e3a-afb7-2feda0bbdb38"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
